# diffusion — Grover 2큐비트 diffusion (H·Z·CZ·H = |00> 반사를 H로 감싼 것)

```python id=bloq
from qualtran import BloqBuilder
from qualtran.bloqs.basic_gates import Hadamard, ZGate, CZ
bb = BloqBuilder()
q0 = bb.add_register("q0", 1); q1 = bb.add_register("q1", 1)
q0 = bb.add(Hadamard(), q=q0); q1 = bb.add(Hadamard(), q=q1)
q0 = bb.add(ZGate(), q=q0);    q1 = bb.add(ZGate(), q=q1)
q0, q1 = bb.add(CZ(), q1=q0, q2=q1)
q0 = bb.add(Hadamard(), q=q0); q1 = bb.add(Hadamard(), q=q1)
bloq = bb.finalize(q0=q0, q1=q1)
```
```python id=golden
import numpy as np
H = np.array([[1, 1], [1, -1]], dtype=complex) / np.sqrt(2)
# D = H⊗H · (2|00><00|−I) · H⊗H,  (2|00><00|−I)=diag(1,-1,-1,-1)
golden = np.kron(H, H) @ np.diag([1, -1, -1, -1]).astype(complex) @ np.kron(H, H)
```
